metadata.name: The difference between the subtleties and the subtle ties
metadata.description:
A vulgar cell division resulting from the deformation of boundaries under pressure.

The algorithm that generates this piece is a spring-based physics simulation with polygon offsetting, constructed with the intention to highlight aspects of the biological process of cell division.

SVG rendered by javascript in the browser, with accompanying signed print
